接口 Dispatcher

  • 所有已知实现类:
    AsyncDispatcher

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
 @InterfaceStability.Evolving
public interface Dispatcher
    Event Dispatcher interface. It dispatches events to registered event handlers based on event types.
